> > > > > > > using has SND_PCM_INFO_RESUME flag,
> > > > > > > dmix->spcm->info has this flag. Then this flag is cleared in
> > > > > > dmix->shmptr->s.info.
> > > > > > >
> > > > > > > 2nd dmix instance:
> > > > > > > snd_pcm_dmix_open()
